  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统的在线协作编辑设计一个状态图，核心场景是学生打开成绩文件时的并发控制。我想从Idle状态开始，当学生打开Education_StudentDB中的文件时进入这个状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "File Opened"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Idle是初始状态。那学生开始编辑后呢？是直接跳转到锁定状态，还是先有一个中间动作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "UserAction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先有一个UserAction状态，叫\"User Edits File\"。学生每输入一个字符就从Idle转移到这个状态。然后需要向Education_GradeSync服务请求锁，我命名为RequestLock。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserAction",
        "RequestLock",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了UserAction和RequestLock。RequestLock这里有个子状态结构，我用花括号包裹。那请求锁之后有两种结果吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RequestLock"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GrantLock和DenyLock两个分支。成功的话返回200 OK，进入LockedState；失败返回409 Conflict，进入ConflictState。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GrantLock",
        "DenyLock",
        "LockedState",
        "ConflictState",
        "200 OK",
        "409 Conflict"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加两个分支。LockedState我命名为\"Locked (Education_StudentDB)\"，里面包含Education_LMS_Portal相关的Editing状态。ConflictState命名为\"Conflict (Education_ClassroomService)\"，关联Education_ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LockedState",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Editing",
        "ConflictState",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "在LockedState内部，Editing状态需要每30秒发送一次Heartbeat心跳，防止学生电脑崩溃导致死锁。心跳会触发ServerUpdate去更新locks表的时间戳。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Editing",
        "Heartbeat",
